              <div style="-webkit-transform:translate3d(0, 0, 0) scale3d(1, 1, 1) rotateX(0) rotateY(0) rotateZ(0DEG) skew(0, 0);-moz-transform:translate3d(0, 0, 0) scale3d(1, 1, 1) rotateX(0) rotateY(0) rotateZ(0DEG) skew(0, 0);-ms-transform:translate3d(0, 0, 0) scale3d(1, 1, 1) rotateX(0) rotateY(0) rotateZ(0DEG) skew(0, 0);transform:translate3d(0, 0, 0) scale3d(1, 1, 1) rotateX(0) rotateY(0) rotateZ(0DEG) skew(0, 0)" class="icon-wrapper"><img src="../../assets/images/Group-38.svg" alt=""></div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <ul style="display:none;opacity:0" role="list" class="accordion-sublist">
            <li class="accordion-sublist-item">
              <div class="faq-content">
                <div class="rich-text-block w-richtext">
                  <p>Contact Support in the app by going to Help =&gt; &quot; I was in a n accident&quot; to submit a report.</p>
                </div>
              </div>
            </li>
          </ul>
        </li>
        <li class="accoridon-list">
          <div data-w-id="a10b6e13-87f3-4f78-c836-78c68d4a8afa" class="faq-header">
            <h5>What do I do if I was hit by a rider?</h5>
            <div style="-webkit-transform:translate3d(0, 0, 0) scale3d(1, 1, 1) rotateX(0) rotateY(0) rotateZ(0DEG) skew(0, 0);-moz-transform:translate3d(0, 0, 0) scale3d(1, 1, 1) rotateX(0) rotateY(0) rotateZ(0DEG) skew(0, 0);-ms-transform:translate3d(0, 0, 0) scale3d(1, 1, 1) rotateX(0) rotateY(0) rotateZ(0DEG) skew(0, 0);transform:translate3d(0, 0, 0) scale3d(1, 1, 1) rotateX(0) rotateY(0) rotateZ(0DEG) skew(0, 0)" class="icon-wrapper">
              <div style="-webkit-transform:translate3d(0, 0, 0) scale3d(1, 1, 1) rotateX(0) rotateY(0) rotateZ(0DEG) skew(0, 0);-moz-transform:translate3d(0, 0, 0) scale3d(1, 1, 1) rotateX(0) rotateY(0) rotateZ(0DEG) skew(0, 0);-ms-transform:translate3d(0, 0, 0) scale3d(1, 1, 1) rotateX(0) rotateY(0) rotateZ(0DEG) skew(0, 0);transform:translate3d(0, 0, 0) scale3d(1, 1, 1) rotateX(0) rotateY(0) rotateZ(0DEG) skew(0, 0)" class="icon-wrapper"><img src="../../assets/images/Group-38.svg" alt=""></div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <ul style="display:none;opacity:0" role="list" class="accordion-sublist">
            <li class="accordion-sublist-item">
              <div class="faq-content">
                <div class="rich-text-block w-richtext">
                  <ol role="list">
                    <li>Exchange contact information with the rider</li>
                    <li>Take photos of the incident including the vehicle, vehicle ID, location etc</li>
                    <li>Secure as much information as you can</li>
                    <li>Once completed, attach all relevant information and email <a href="mailto:accident@li.me">accident@li.me</a>
                    </li>
                  </ol>
                </div>
              </div>
            </li>
          </ul>
        </li>
        <li class="accoridon-list">
          <div data-w-id="a10b6e13-87f3-4f78-c836-78c68d4a8b10" class="faq-header">
            <h5>Do I have to wear a helmet when I ride?</h5>
            <div style="-webkit-transform:translate3d(0, 0, 0) scale3d(1, 1, 1) rotateX(0) rotateY(0) rotateZ(0DEG) skew(0, 0);-moz-transform:translate3d(0, 0, 0) scale3d(1, 1, 1) rotateX(0) rotateY(0) rotateZ(0DEG) skew(0, 0);-ms-transform:translate3d(0, 0, 0) scale3d(1, 1, 1) rotateX(0) rotateY(0) rotateZ(0DEG) skew(0, 0);transform:translate3d(0, 0, 0) scale3d(1, 1, 1) rotateX(0) rotateY(0) rotateZ(0DEG) skew(0, 0)" class="icon-wrapper">
              <div style="-webkit-transform:translate3d(0, 0, 0) scale3d(1, 1, 1) rotateX(0) rotateY(0) rotateZ(0DEG) skew(0, 0);-moz-transform:translate3d(0, 0, 0) scale3d(1, 1, 1) rotateX(0) rotateY(0) rotateZ(0DEG) skew(0, 0);-ms-transform:translate3d(0, 0, 0) scale3d(1, 1, 1) rotateX(0) rotateY(0) rotateZ(0DEG) skew(0, 0);transform:translate3d(0, 0, 0) scale3d(1, 1, 1) rotateX(0) rotateY(0) rotateZ(0DEG) skew(0, 0)" class="icon-wrapper"><img src="../../assets/images/Group-38.svg" alt=""></div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <ul style="display:none;opacity:0" role="list" class="accordion-sublist">
            <li class="accordion-sublist-item">
              <div class="faq-content">
                <div class="rich-text-block w-richtext">
                  <p>Please always wear a helmet, even if the regulations vary depending on the region, country and location.</p>
                </div>
              </div>
            </li>
          </ul>
        </li>
      </ul>
    </div>
  </div>
 {% endblock %}